title: When You Have That Urge To Eat Too Much
itunes:title: When You Have That Urge To Eat Too Much
description:
On today's podcast we both tell stories about urges to overeat. We both experienced feeling satisfied in our stomachs but NOT in our minds. We knew we didn't need more food, but we just wanted to KEEP eating.
 
Listen in to watch us think about what was actually happening around us and how we resolved the urges.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
